  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe Display settings dont perisist after a reboot.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n- Go to Settings-->Privacy&Security-->Privacy\r\n- Set the Display settings to 'On'\r\n- SignOut & Quit\r\n- SignIn again\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n- The changed settings should persist\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n- The changed settings dont persist \r\nhttps://www.loom.com/share/d8b80a286e9740e7b8a9e328ff2cb23c\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nThis appears to only affect both the Display settings\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version : base_bc , commit : fc8b4211aa974296cceaabe093ff402b28f17dab\r\n",
